>>> +Naming convention for files and command line options
>>> +----------------------------------------------------
>>> +
>>> +'-' should be used to separate words in commandline options and filenames.
>>> +E.g. timer-works.
>>> +
>>> +Note that some of the options and filenames are using '_'. This is now
